# Normalize line endings. Store text as LF in the repository and check it out
# as LF on every platform, so editors/tools (vitest snapshots, Prettier) on
# Windows stop churning CRLF<->LF regardless of each contributor's core.autocrlf.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets git must never touch (line-ending or diff filters).
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.pdf binary
